HEADWORD: Water devil
<hw>Wa"ter dev"il</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The
rapacious larva of a large water beetle (<spn>Hydrophilus piceus</spn>),
and of other similar species. See <xex>Illust.</xex> of Water
beetle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

